## NON-NEGOTIABLE OUTPUT RULES (SUMMARY)

| Requirement | Rule |
|---|---|
| All headings | `clamp()` — NEVER hardcoded px/rem |
| All nav menus | hamburger button + JS toggle + `aria-expanded` |
| All grids | collapse to 1-column at 768px |
| All DOM queries | null-checked before use |
| All scroll listeners | `{ passive: true }` |
| SPA routes on Vercel | `vercel.json` with rewrites (mandatory for R3F) |
| All images | descriptive `alt` text |
| Every page | identical nav + footer HTML |
| THREE.js renderer | `setPixelRatio(Math.min(devicePixelRatio, 2))` |
| Every 3D scene | WebGL detection + 2D CSS fallback |
| All GLTF models | Draco-compressed, max 5 MB |
| Mobile screens | postprocessing disabled below 768px |

